241
00:14:13,000 --> 00:14:15,530
Lebih ramai orang patut tahu tentang
Pulau Xingpu.

242
00:14:16,120 --> 00:14:17,050
Dan awak,

243
00:14:17,480 --> 00:14:18,440
He Xiangyong,

244
00:14:19,400 --> 00:14:20,870
